@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<head>
    <title>About Us</title>
    <!-- AOS CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://images.rawpixel.com/image_1300/cHJpdmF0ZS9sci9pbWFnZXMvd2Vic2l0ZS8yMDIyLTA2L3YxMTYtYWdyaWN1bHR1cmUtMDJlXzEuanBn.jpg');
            background-position: center top;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 70px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: black;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .title span.green {
            color: #024d0a;
        }

        .paragraph,
        .mission-paragraph {
            font-size: 26px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #333;
        }

        .trusted-by {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .providers {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 100px;
        }

        .providers img {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .mission-title {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: #ff8400;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .Join-title {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: #024d0a;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .founders-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .founders-title {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #024d0a;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .founders {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 70px;
        }

        .founder {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .founder img {
            width: 400px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .founder-role {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: black;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .offices-section,
        .contact-section,
        .image-banner {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .contact-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .contact-form {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact-form form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .form-group {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 280px;
        }

        .full-width {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact-form label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .contact-form input,
        .contact-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #fefefe;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-form input:focus,
        .contact-form textarea:focus {
            border-color: #024d0a;
            outline: none;
        }

        .contact-form textarea {
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .contact-form button {
            align-self: flex-start;
            background-color: #024d0a;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e57;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="title" data-aos="fade-down">
        Changing Southern Africa <span class="green">Together</span>
    </div>

    <div class="paragraph" data-aos="fade-up">
        Collaboration fuels progress at AgriConnect, and we see it as essential for South Africa's agricultural future.
        We connect farmers, employees, and industry stakeholders on a platform designed for knowledge sharing and joint
        efforts toward sustainability and prosperity. Partner with us to reshape agriculture through unity and mutual
        support.
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="mission-title" data-aos="fade-left">
        Our goal: Help Southern Africa's agriculture access
    </div>
    <div class="mission-paragraph" data-aos="fade-right">
        At AgriConnect, we're committed to transforming South African agriculture by breaking down existing barriers and
        leveling the playing field. We provide essential resources and knowledge to all stakeholders, cultivating an
        inclusive and supportive space that drives enhanced productivity, sustainability, and innovation. Our dedication
        lies in empowering local farmers, championing sustainable practices, and ensuring every member of the
        agricultural community has the opportunity to flourish.
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="offices-section" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <div class="mission-title">
            Our Presence in Southern Africa & Beyond
        </div>
        <div class="mission-paragraph" data-aos="zoom-in"></div>>
        Headquartered in Durban and Eastern Cape, South Africa, AgriEnergy supports clients both locally and across
        the globe. Through our flexible remote work model, we collaborate with professionals and partners from
        various regions across South Africa.
    </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="image-banner" data-aos="zoom-in-up">
        <img src="~/images/banner.png" alt="AgriEnergy Banner"
            style="width: 100%; max-width: 1300px; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto;" />
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="contact-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="Join-title">Any Questions? Drop Us a Message</div>

        <div class="contact-form">
            <form method="post" action="#">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <label for="message">Message</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" placeholder="How can we help you?"
                        required></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <!-- AOS JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({
            duration: 1000,
            once: true
        });
    </script>
</body>
